02:04:36,854 --> 02:05:02,977
Tim was, we sat down with the water department. We said, okay, as this model is made and as you guys get the data, share it with us. And then we'll have that data. It's on maps. We'll know what size water main is there. Currently right now, we have, you know, very little idea of what we're hooking up to. We just hook up to a height and hopefully it's okay, right? So once we hook up to it, we know, but by that time it's too late. So it'd be nice to be able to, as we're coming into the scene, okay,

